long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Snooze your tabs until later.

Be extremely more productive by snoozing non-urgent tabs to a later time. By getting the distracting tabs out of the way you gain a clean mental workspace, allowing you to focus better and get the important things done. When it's time, the tabs will automatically open in the background.
